phBadBehave is a phpBB3 plugin based on http://bad-behavior.ioerror.us/ which prevents bots to access your forum.

More details here : http://bad-behavior.ioerror.us/about/


For Installation details please see the install.xml file.

You can open it with any modern Webbrowser.

v2.0.2:
- Supports Bad Behave 2.2.15
- Tooltips on keys in search and overview pages

v2.0.1:
- Fix a bug using MODX 1.2.6

v2.0.0:
- Support Bad Behave 2.2.14

v1.0 and before:
- Developed by initial author https://github.com/philnate/phBadBehave
